---
title: Wasabi-Glazed Steak with Soba Noodle Salad & Creamy Avocado-Lime Dressing
description: Everything's better with avocado, right? We certainly think so! Creamy avocado makes a luscious no-cook dressing in this cold soba salad. Soy, beef stock, wasabi, and garlic become an intensly flavored glaze to finish off seared steak. Have your own chopsticks? This is the time to use them!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/55253d9b6ced6e174e8b45a5.jpg
